32struct WMOAreaTableTripple
33{
34 WMOAreaTableTripple(int32_t r, int32_t a, int32_t g) : groupId(g), rootId(r), adtId(a) { }
35
36 bool operator <(const WMOAreaTableTripple& b) const
37 {
38 return memcmp(this, &b, sizeof(WMOAreaTableTripple)) < 0;
39 }
40
41 int32_t groupId;
42 int32_t rootId;
43 int32_t adtId;
44};

1084#define MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS 4
1085 struct FactionTemplateEntry
1086 {
1087 uint32_t ID; // 0
1088 uint32_t Faction; // 1
1089 uint32_t FactionGroup; // 2
1090 uint32_t Mask; // 3
1091 uint32_t FriendlyMask; // 4
1092 uint32_t HostileMask; // 5
1093 uint32_t EnemyFactions[MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS]; // 6-9
1094 uint32_t FriendlyFactions[MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS]; // 10-13
1095
1096 // Helpers
1097 bool isFriendlyTo(FactionTemplateEntry const& entry) const
1098 {
1099 if (entry.Faction)
1100 {
1101 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS; ++i)
1102 if (EnemyFactions[i] == entry.Faction)
1103 return false;
1104 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS; ++i)
1105 if (FriendlyFactions[i] == entry.Faction)
1106 return true;
1107 }
1108 return (FriendlyMask & entry.Mask) || (Mask & entry.FriendlyMask);
1109 }
1110 bool isHostileTo(FactionTemplateEntry const& entry) const
1111 {
1112 if (entry.Faction)
1113 {
1114 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS; ++i)
1115 if (EnemyFactions[i] == entry.Faction)
1116 return true;
1117 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS; ++i)
1118 if (FriendlyFactions[i] == entry.Faction)
1119 return false;
1120 }
1121 return (HostileMask & entry.Mask) != 0;
1122 }
1123 bool isHostileToPlayers() const { return (HostileMask & FACTION_MASK_PLAYER) != 0; }
1124 bool isNeutralToAll() const
1125 {
1126 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_FACTION_RELATIONS; ++i)
1127 if (EnemyFactions[i] != 0)
1128 return false;
1129 return HostileMask == 0 && FriendlyMask == 0;
1130 }
1131 bool isContestedGuardFaction() const { return (FactionGroup & FACTION_TEMPLATE_FLAG_CONTESTED_GUARD) != 0; }
1132 };

2413 bool hasFlag(VehicleSeatFlags flag) const { return (flags & flag) != 0; }
2414 bool hasFlag(VehicleSeatFlagsB flag) const { return (flagsB & flag) != 0; }
2415
2416 bool IsUsable() const
2417 {
2418 if ((flags & VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_USABLE) != 0)
2419 return true;
2420 return false;
2421 }
2422
2423 bool IsController() const
2424 {
2425 if ((flags & VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_CAN_CONTROL) != 0)
2426 return true;
2427 return false;
2428 }
2429
2430 bool HidesPassenger() const
2431 {
2432 if ((flags & VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_HIDE_PASSENGER) != 0)
2433 return true;
2434 return false;
2435 }
2436
2437 bool canEnterOrExit() const { return hasFlag(VehicleSeatFlags(VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_USABLE | VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_CAN_CONTROL | VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_SHOULD_USE_VEH_SEAT_EXIT_ANIM_ON_VOLUNTARY_EXIT)); }
2438 bool canSwitchFromSeat() const { return hasFlag(VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_CAN_SWITCH); }
2439 bool isUsableByOverride() const {
2440 return hasFlag(VehicleSeatFlags(VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_UNCONTROLLED | VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_UNK18))
2441 || hasFlag(VehicleSeatFlagsB(VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_B_USABLE_FORCED | VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_B_USABLE_FORCED_2 |
2442 VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_B_USABLE_FORCED_3 | VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_B_USABLE_FORCED_4));
2443 }
2444 bool isEjectable() const { return hasFlag(VEHICLE_SEAT_FLAG_B_EJECTABLE); }
2445 };
